And the final push, for those who take killing as their job, after being assigned with a contract, is it worth asking the client why?

Trash movie only made for kids and childish tards. Yet 8.0 point on IMDB, along with the famous "Man of Steel" with the main protagonist playing a statue the whole movie.

Title: John Wick: Chapter 2 Official Trailer #1 (2017) Keanu Reeves Action Movie HD
Comment:
Two things

1. I hope to god this one is as good, or better then the 1st one. I feel, looking at the recent trailers, they kind of went bigger, but it still seems contained (Rome/Vatican setting). I always felt partly why the 1st one worked, was how "self-contained" and "restrained" everything was, to choreography/story and acting. 

2. If they are gonna make this some kinda saga(which it kinda looks like), I hope they keep it to 3 films. Films like these are character driven (John Wick himself), so I hope they don't overdo it a 100 sequels, and destroy the mystery of his character. :/This has happened to too many iconic characters (Freddy Kruger, Jason, Neo etc...)

So with that said, I'm SUPER excited about this prequel! Woop woop!

I will wait, maybe someday Keanu will make good action/revenge movie, ill pass on Wick this is only for comic fans.
